ibrdtn (0.6.5) stable; urgency=low

  * Wrong CBHE parsing fixed.
  * C++ API: Added method to get the timestamp of a bundle
  * Bundle Security Protocol
    * Serialization fixed
    * PCB: Store the integrity check value in the right TLV
